column5: We now have three skins available. There are the two we are used to, Club and Driftwood, but we now also have the faster loading plain-Jane 'IPB 2.2.0 Default' skin. If you are on dial-up you may want to use that one.There's two more left to do, Spiels favourite 'Reflections' and a new skin for our more feminine members.
When we get to four, let me know.  I've always wanted to have one.
